{"tid":2053566,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［跳船保平安？］足總證實機構管治總監胡子慶已請辭ㅤ不會出席帳委會聆訊","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T11:59:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b8a5ac8f7ad8ad33f02b9abbe7e779ea52f81f","tid":2053566,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"【體路專訊】近日陷入管治風波的足總今日（6 日）證實，年薪過百萬的機構管治總監胡子慶已經請辭，目前正處離職前休假，下星期一亦不會出席立法會帳委會公開聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n審計報告早前揭發足總多項管治問題，包括轄下審計委員會自 2015 年起四年半來未曾組成及開會、招聘及招標程序出問題等。足總昨日在帳委會聆訊中披露，機構管治總監胡子慶年薪逾百萬。早前曾有傳媒追問胡子慶，但他並無回應自己有否失職，公民黨議員陳淑莊要求胡子慶出席下周一的聆訊，當時主席貝鈞奇指會邀請對方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/sport/%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3-%E8%B6%B3%E7%B8%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%AE%A1%E6%B2%BB%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%E8%83%A1%E5%AD%90%E6%85%B6%E5%B7%B2%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%B8%B3%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3-%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=16c0fbb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsport%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B6%25B3-%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=745ba67d\" targ